title.narrative: West Africa Regional Transport and Transit Facilitation Project

description.narrative: The project is expected to support the implementation of the first phase the WAEMU/Ghana’s Road Program I (RP-I) program. This program is intended to facilitate transport and transit on the Tema -- Ouagadougou -- Bamako corridor as a pilot for other priority corridors.
